<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto p-3 md:p-6 bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 text-black dark:text-white transition-colors duration-300"
     data-controller="exercise-checker fill-blanks auto-advance text-toggle font-controls"
     data-page-viewer-image-url-value="<%= asset_path('bus3_mat/p028/page.png') %>"
     data-text-toggle-target="content"
     data-font-controls-target="content">

  <!-- Header -->
  <%= render 'shared/page_header', pagina: @pagina %>

  <!-- Esercizio 1: Box azzurro con due esempi -->
  <div class="bg-[#C7EAFB] dark:bg-cyan-900/40 p-4 md:p-6 -ml-3 md:-ml-0 -mr-3 md:mr-0 mb-8">
    <div class="flex items-start gap-3 mb-6">
      <div class="bg-red-500 text-white rounded-full w-8 h-8 flex items-center justify-center font-bold flex-shrink-0">
        1
      </div>
      <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">
        <strong>Ricordi quando usi la sottrazione? Leggi e completa.</strong>
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
      <!-- Per calcolare il resto -->
      <div>
        <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200 mb-4">
          <span class="text-red-500">●</span> Per calcolare il <span class="font-bold text-cyan-600 dark:text-cyan-400">resto</span>.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200 mb-4">
          La maestra Claudia ha 160 fogli. Ne usa 120 per fare le fotocopie. Quanti fogli le restano?
        </p>
        <div class="flex justify-center">
          <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 border-2 border-cyan-400 dark:border-cyan-500 rounded-lg p-3 inline-flex items-center gap-2 flex-wrap">
            <input type="text" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-correct-answer="160"
                   class="w-16 px-2 py-1 border-b-2 border-dotted border-gray-400 text-center font-bold bg-transparent dark:text-white"
                   maxlength="3" inputmode="numeric">
            <span class="dark:text-white">-</span>
            <input type="text" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-correct-answer="120"
                   class="w-16 px-2 py-1 border-b-2 border-dotted border-gray-400 text-center font-bold bg-transparent dark:text-white"
                   maxlength="3" inputmode="numeric">
            <span class="dark:text-white">=</span>
            <input type="text" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-correct-answer="40"
                   class="w-16 px-2 py-1 border-b-2 border-dotted border-gray-400 text-center font-bold bg-transparent dark:text-white"
                   maxlength="2" inputmode="numeric">
            <span class="dark:text-white">fogli</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Per calcolare la differenza -->
      <div>
        <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200 mb-4">
          <span class="text-red-500">●</span> Per calcolare la <span class="font-bold text-cyan-600 dark:text-cyan-400">differenza</span>.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200 mb-4">
          Sulla spiaggia ci sono 10 conchiglie gialle e 3 conchiglie blu. Quante sono in più le conchiglie gialle? Quante sono in meno le conchiglie blu? Qual è la differenza?
        </p>
        <div class="mb-4 bg-white rounded-xl p-2">
          <%= image_tag "bus3_mat/p028/output-1743504902028_603_431_347_100.png",
              alt: "Conchiglie",
              class: "max-w-full w-full" %>
        </div>
        <div class="flex justify-center">
          <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 border-2 border-cyan-400 dark:border-cyan-500 rounded-lg p-3 inline-flex items-center gap-2 flex-wrap">
            <input type="text" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-correct-answer="10"
                   class="w-12 px-2 py-1 border-b-2 border-dotted border-gray-400 text-center font-bold bg-transparent dark:text-white"
                   maxlength="2" inputmode="numeric">
            <span class="dark:text-white">-</span>
            <input type="text" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-correct-answer="3"
                   class="w-12 px-2 py-1 border-b-2 border-dotted border-gray-400 text-center font-bold bg-transparent dark:text-white"
                   maxlength="1" inputmode="numeric">
            <span class="dark:text-white">=</span>
            <input type="text" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-correct-answer="7"
                   class="w-12 px-2 py-1 border-b-2 border-dotted border-gray-400 text-center font-bold bg-transparent dark:text-white"
                   maxlength="1" inputmode="numeric">
            <span class="dark:text-white">conchiglie</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Esercizio 2: Risolvi i problemi -->
  <div class="bg-transparent p-4 md:p-8 mb-8">
    <div class="flex items-start gap-3 mb-6">
      <div class="bg-red-500 text-white rounded-full w-8 h-8 flex items-center justify-center font-bold flex-shrink-0">
        2
      </div>
      <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">
        <strong>Risolvi i problemi.</strong>
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-x-8 gap-y-10">
      <!-- Problema a -->
      <div>
        <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200 mb-4">
          <span class="font-bold text-orange-600">a.</span> Sara ha un puzzle da 254 pezzi. Ne ha già sistemati 132. Quanti pezzi deve ancora sistemare per finire il puzzle?
        </p>
        <div class="flex justify-center">
          <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 border-2 border-cyan-400 dark:border-cyan-500 rounded-lg p-3 inline-flex items-center gap-2 flex-wrap">
            <input type="text" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-correct-answer="254"
                   class="w-16 px-2 py-1 border-b-2 border-dotted border-gray-400 text-center font-bold bg-transparent dark:text-white"
                   maxlength="3" inputmode="numeric">
            <span class="dark:text-white">-</span>
            <input type="text" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-correct-answer="132"
                   class="w-16 px-2 py-1 border-b-2 border-dotted border-gray-400 text-center font-bold bg-transparent dark:text-white"
                   maxlength="3" inputmode="numeric">
            <span class="dark:text-white">=</span>
            <input type="text" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-correct-answer="122"
                   class="w-16 px-2 py-1 border-b-2 border-dotted border-gray-400 text-center font-bold bg-transparent dark:text-white"
                   maxlength="3" inputmode="numeric">
            <span class="dark:text-white">pezzi</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Problema c -->
      <div>
        <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200 mb-4">
          <span class="font-bold text-orange-600">c.</span> Sul pulmino della scuola salgono 22 tra bambini e bambine. Alla prima fermata ne scendono 6. Quanti bambini e bambine sono ancora sul pulmino?
        </p>
        <div class="flex justify-center">
          <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 border-2 border-cyan-400 dark:border-cyan-500 rounded-lg p-3 inline-flex items-center gap-2 flex-wrap">
            <input type="text" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-correct-answer="22"
                   class="w-12 px-2 py-1 border-b-2 border-dotted border-gray-400 text-center font-bold bg-transparent dark:text-white"
                   maxlength="2" inputmode="numeric">
            <span class="dark:text-white">-</span>
            <input type="text" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-correct-answer="6"
                   class="w-12 px-2 py-1 border-b-2 border-dotted border-gray-400 text-center font-bold bg-transparent dark:text-white"
                   maxlength="1" inputmode="numeric">
            <span class="dark:text-white">=</span>
            <input type="text" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-correct-answer="16"
                   class="w-12 px-2 py-1 border-b-2 border-dotted border-gray-400 text-center font-bold bg-transparent dark:text-white"
                   maxlength="2" inputmode="numeric">
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Problema b -->
      <div>
        <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200 mb-4">
          <span class="font-bold text-orange-600">b.</span> La squadra di calcio in cui gioca Matteo quest'anno ha segnato 18 goal, quella di Gabriele ne ha segnati 23. Quanti goal in più ha segnato la squadra di Gabriele?
        </p>
        <div class="flex justify-center">
          <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 border-2 border-cyan-400 dark:border-cyan-500 rounded-lg p-3 inline-flex items-center gap-2 flex-wrap">
            <input type="text" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-correct-answer="23"
                   class="w-12 px-2 py-1 border-b-2 border-dotted border-gray-400 text-center font-bold bg-transparent dark:text-white"
                   maxlength="2" inputmode="numeric">
            <span class="dark:text-white">-</span>
            <input type="text" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-correct-answer="18"
                   class="w-12 px-2 py-1 border-b-2 border-dotted border-gray-400 text-center font-bold bg-transparent dark:text-white"
                   maxlength="2" inputmode="numeric">
            <span class="dark:text-white">=</span>
            <input type="text" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-correct-answer="5"
                   class="w-12 px-2 py-1 border-b-2 border-dotted border-gray-400 text-center font-bold bg-transparent dark:text-white"
                   maxlength="1" inputmode="numeric">
            <span class="dark:text-white">goal</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Problema d -->
      <div>
        <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200 mb-4">
          <span class="font-bold text-orange-600">d.</span> In un albergo sono presenti 64 ospiti. Alle 10 del mattino 42 ospiti lasciano l'albergo. Quanti ospiti rimangono?
        </p>
        <div class="flex justify-center">
          <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 border-2 border-cyan-400 dark:border-cyan-500 rounded-lg p-3 inline-flex items-center gap-2 flex-wrap">
            <input type="text" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-correct-answer="64"
                   class="w-12 px-2 py-1 border-b-2 border-dotted border-gray-400 text-center font-bold bg-transparent dark:text-white"
                   maxlength="2" inputmode="numeric">
            <span class="dark:text-white">-</span>
            <input type="text" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-correct-answer="42"
                   class="w-12 px-2 py-1 border-b-2 border-dotted border-gray-400 text-center font-bold bg-transparent dark:text-white"
                   maxlength="2" inputmode="numeric">
            <span class="dark:text-white">=</span>
            <input type="text" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-correct-answer="22"
                   class="w-12 px-2 py-1 border-b-2 border-dotted border-gray-400 text-center font-bold bg-transparent dark:text-white"
                   maxlength="2" inputmode="numeric">
            <span class="dark:text-white">ospiti</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Footer con controlli -->
  <%= render 'shared/exercise_controls', color: 'cyan' %>
</div>
